s\nbehavior vary to a large extent independently and could for example be the mass\naccretion rate through the disk and the size of a Comptonizing region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2000 19:02:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 17 Sep 2000 14:52:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
