ic\nclouds. In the context of a standard CDM cosmology, $M_{\\rm SB}$ lies between\n1$\\sigma$ and 2$\\sigma$ density fluctuations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jan 2000 08:10:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
